lead_paragraph: George Hincapie took the individual title and his Discovery Channel team finished second, in its final United States event before disbanding, in the six-day Tour of Missouri. Ivan Dominguez of Toyota-United took his second stage of the tour in a mass sprint, finishing in 2 hours 37 minutes 13 seconds.
